title: Silver Two looking for Gold Duo Partner!
body:
Hey Guys

I'm in silver two and really wanna get to gold, I main mid although I have spent some time trying to play adc.
I am looking for a Gold duo partner to help raise me up. :D 
I have improved a lot since making this montage and have been to bronze, that showed me how much your attitude really affects the game; 
now I'm back in silver two, looking at getting into gold. I think a duo partner would be a great help!

Add me in league if you're interested at ENTYON

replies.body:
Nice montage. Watching your video i really like your aggressive style. I too am an aggressive playmaker.

Im not Gold, but i am Silver 2. And i am pretty motivated to climb.

Im free after 6pm because of work, so add me Noblesse :)
Hey, thanks for the message and I added you. should be fun to duo :D

Hey mate, im silver 1, Adc main. looking for a duo to reach gold. clearly you think you have what it takes and I'm pretty determined also. see how we play together. 
Message me

Aus Dave
